      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3841 - Sama'ah asked him about purchasing stolen or embezzled goods.\nImam (as) said: \"If you know that it is so, then no, unless it is something you are buying from the authorities.\""
        ]
